      "widgets_values": [
        "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<h2>MODELS AND NODES USED IN THIS WORKFLOW</h2><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #666666\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"model-v1\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Remove Background Pixaroma</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><p><strong>You can use 3 Different Models:</strong></p><p>\\n\\n</p><p><strong><em>birefnet.safetensors (Standard) - Needs 4-6 GB VRAM</em></strong></p><p>\\n\\n</p><ul>\\n  <li>Internal resolution: 1024\u00d71024</li>\\n  <li>Best for: clean objects, products, logos. Fast everyday cutouts.</li>\\n</ul><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-dl\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #f66744\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/BiRefNet/resolve/main/background_removal/birefnet.safetensors\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Download birefnet.safetensors<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnsize\\\">424 MB</span></a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><div class=\\\"pix-note-folderhint\\\" style=\\\"color: #888888\\\">Place in: ComfyUI/models/background_removal</div><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-dashed\\\" style=\\\"color: #666666\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><p><strong><em>birefnet-hr.safetensors (High Resolution) - Needs 8 GB+ VRAM</em></strong></p><p>\\n\\n</p><ul>\\n  <li>Internal resolution: 2048\u00d72048</li>\\n  <li>Best for: large images needing fine outline detail.</li>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"warning-v1\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;After download, rename <code>model.safetensors</code> to <code>birefnet-hr.safetensors</code></li>\\n</ul><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-dl\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #f66744\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/ZhengPeng7/BiRefNet_HR/resolve/main/model.safetensors\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Download birefnet-hr.safetensors<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnsize\\\">444 MB</span></a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><div class=\\\"pix-note-folderhint\\\" style=\\\"color: #888888\\\">Place in: ComfyUI/models/background_removal</div><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-dashed\\\" style=\\\"color: #666666\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><p><strong><em>birefnet-matting.safetensors (Soft Alpha Edges) - Needs 8 GB+ VRAM</em></strong></p><p>\\n\\n</p><ul>\\n  <li>Internal resolution: 2048\u00d72048</li>\\n  <li>Best for: hair, fur, lace, soft fabric, glass, smoke, and sheer materials.</li>\\n  <li><span data-ic=\\\"warning-v1\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;After download, rename <code>model.safetensors</code> to <code>birefnet-matting.safetensors</code></li>\\n</ul><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-dl\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #f66744\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/ZhengPeng7/BiRefNet_HR-matting/resolve/main/model.safetensors\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Download birefnet-matting.safetensors<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnsize\\\">444 MB</span></a>\\n</span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><div class=\\\"pix-note-folderhint\\\" style=\\\"color: #888888\\\">Place in: ComfyUI/models/background_removal</div><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #666666\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><p><span data-ic=\\\"warning-v1\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;After placing the files, <span style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\">restart</span> ComfyUI or refresh model lists using <span style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\">R</span> shortcut.</p><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #666666\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"nodes-installed\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Custom Nodes</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><ul>\\n  <li>Pixaroma</li>\\n</ul><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #666666\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"pixaroma\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Resources</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><p>\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-discord\\\" href=\\\"https://discord.com/invite/gggpkVgBf3\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Join Discord</a>&nbsp;\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-yt\\\" href=\\\"https://www.youtube.com/@pixaroma\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Pixaroma YouTube Channel</a>&nbsp;\\n</p>\",\"buttonColor\":\"#f66744\",\"lineColor\":\"#f66744\",\"width\":557.087617540421,\"height\":818.4429544967918,\"backgroundColor\":\"#2a2a2a\"}",
